metric.description:
The metric to report on.
Supports two types of metrics:
"count": count records/entries (does not require attribute_path): {"type":"count"}
"attribute": aggregate a numeric attribute (number/currency) with sum/mean/min/max/count:
- {"type":"attribute","attribute_path":[["companies","employee_count"]],"aggregation":"sum"}
- {"type":"attribute","attribute_path":[["deals","value"]],"aggregation":"mean"}
Aggregation happens after filter and before grouping.
format: metric object
